        "created_at": "2022-11-04T12:16:49.217Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m like David, I tend to drink my Beaujolais young and within 5 years of release.  Unlike David, I do that with Kabinett as well!  I do tend to age the Roilette Cuvee Tardive and the Griffe du Marquis bottlings, and think these show best with 10 or so years on them.</p>",
